INSERT INTO "submissions_dpquestion_2009" VALUES(9447,461,'1','2008','No','2009','No','Q1: Nigeria signed on to the global IHP+ compact in May 2008 hence the baseline year of 2008. The  Country Compact has been developed and finalized through a wide stakeholder participatory process.  Government clearance processes have also been concluded. The next step  is endorsement by government and partner signatories. The country compact is a timebound document for the period 2010 - 2015 in support of the National Health Plan for the same period.');
INSERT INTO "submissions_dpquestion_2009" VALUES(9448,461,'2','2007','9247012.0','2009','12401453.0','Q2. UNFPA for the period 2003 - 2007 supported Nigeria with development assistance of over $40m. In 2008 being a bridging year between CPs, the CO spent about $10m. For the current CP 2009 - 2012, UNFPA is expected to disburse about $64m. UNFPA provided Reproductive Health commodities, Capacity building activities for health workers, health policies and plans, M&E, demand creation activities at community levels. Q3. UNFPA is not involved in Direct budget support and as such its development assistance is not reported on national health sector budgets.');
